results.name: Expansion of the polynomial (1+x^3)*(1+x^15)*(1+x^23)*(1+x^27)*(1+x^35)*(1+x^39)*(1+x^47)*(1+x^59).
comment: This is the Poincaré polynomial for the Lie group E_8.
reference: Borel, A. and Chevalley, C., The Betti numbers of the exceptional groups, Mem. Amer. Math. Soc. 1955, no. 14, pp 1-9.
